{"tid":685612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逆線行駛撞傷途人　休班警被控危險駕駛","createTime":"2018-05-31T14:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T16:22:04.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"166bcd98ffd2492e1f8732b0f2ad7f74793c0e4c","tid":685612,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"一名46歲姓何的休班警務人員，去年12月5日在灣仔道136號對開，駕駛電單車懷疑逆線行駛，撞傷一名35歲外籍女子。她腳部受傷清醒，其後送往東區醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n警方深入調查案件及徵詢法律意見後，昨日將涉事司機拘捕，並落案控以一項「危險駕駛引致他人身體受嚴重傷害」罪，案件將於周五（6月1日）在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理。"},{"pid":"0f0e46f2a7fa934b9b31fe1953b66d25dd5b759c","tid":685612,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180531/s00001/1527774004395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180531%2Fs00001%2F1527774004395&d=d4UG9qIz8L5t1376%2FBmfqPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=140bb7e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180531%2Fs00001%2F1527774004395&h=38bea564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180531/s00001/1527774004395</a>"},{"pid":"2f9f033b8e437365a4c5b70710a3a5bff35ce5d4","tid":685612,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"阿sir揸車唔使你教"},{"pid":"4359a678e0425971f0bd8a7f1f97f4bdcf5c90f3","tid":685612,"uid":55531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"盧偉聰指一個疏忽足以影響另一家庭　籲負責任態度駕駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c66fcf1b53e6a4f9e68ef04a6c478bd1d72752b","tid":685612,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"警方發言人表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理。"},{"pid":"1